!! 2 Distinctions
!!! Intermediate State (Temporary Heaven) vs The Eternal State (Eternal Heaven)

This is where heaven exists right now. When you have a family members that pass away, they go to the intermediate state. Scripture says that this heaven doesn't last forever. This heaven isn't bad, heaven is great. What does Scripture say about this temporary heaven? Scripture calls this the abode of God.

